The paper proposes an automated system for epilepsy detection using EEG brain signals based on deep learning approach. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computer Science related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
